data.description: Opportunity abounds!!! If you want a cozy 2 bedroom, 1 bath with the potential of finishing the shop for an office, hobby room, or??? All for less the $300k, this one's for you. This property is also zoned Low Density (LDR) which means you have possibilities of adding an ADU, or maybe tear everything down and building a duplex, triplex, or quad? Buyer must do their own due diligence and check with city for zoning possibilities.This is a great sized city lot just waiting for your touches. Come see it today!
